'''Jintigi (Ogya) Afahyɛ''' yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a Ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Gonja mpotam a ɛwɔ Sare so Mantam no mu, kane Atifi Mantam no mu wɔ Ghana di. Damango a ɛyɛ Gonjaman kuropɔn yɛ nea ɛsɛ wa’ni wo afahyɛ no bere mu. Wodi saa afahyɛ wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so nnan no mu<ref>https://ghanaemberlin.de/travel-tourism/festival/</ref><ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref><ref>http://www.gattagh.com/events.html</ref><ref name="touringghana.com">https://touringghana.com/northern-region/</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔ afahyɛ no bere no mu no, wɔde nkanea to santene fa nkuro, nkura ne nwura a ɛwɔ Gonjaman no mu. Wɔkenkan Koran saa bere no de kankye hwɛ nea ebesi wɔ afe a edi ho no mu<ref name="touringghana.com"/><ref>http://ghanakey.com/ghana-festivals.html</ref><ref>https://www.fiandadghanalimited.com/jintigi-fire-festival/</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
